518
00:25:35,700 --> 00:25:37,319
[SPEAKER_02] a ne što je bio u domovinskom ratu

519
00:25:37,319 --> 00:25:38,339
[SPEAKER_02] kao bližoj prošlosti.

520
00:25:38,339 --> 00:25:41,220
[SPEAKER_02] I Hrvatska država se prema tom pozdravu

521
00:25:41,220 --> 00:25:42,400
[SPEAKER_02] više ponaša prema tome

522
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,660
[SPEAKER_02] što je on značio u ratu

523
00:25:43,660 --> 00:25:45,180
[SPEAKER_02] koji nema veze s Hrvatskom državom,

524
00:25:45,180 --> 00:25:47,240
[SPEAKER_02] nego prema tome što je on značio u ratu

525
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:49,099
[SPEAKER_02] koji je bio konstitutivan

526
00:25:49,099 --> 00:25:50,700
[SPEAKER_02] za suvremenu Hrvatsku državu.

527
00:25:50,700 --> 00:25:51,539
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

528
00:25:51,539 --> 00:25:52,619
[SPEAKER_02] normalno je da simboli

529
00:25:52,619 --> 00:25:53,859
