534
00:25:59,180 --> 00:26:01,259
[SPEAKER_02] pozitivno hinduističkog simbola

535
00:26:01,259 --> 00:26:02,319
[SPEAKER_02] postala negativna

536
00:26:02,319 --> 00:26:03,519
