537
00:26:03,519 --> 00:26:05,880
[SPEAKER_02] onda se mogu i dekontaminirati.

538
00:26:05,880 --> 00:26:06,220
[SPEAKER_02] Dakle,

539
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:07,160
