624
00:27:49,319 --> 00:27:52,420
[SPEAKER_04] Imaš pola sata.

625
00:27:52,420 --> 00:27:53,839
[SPEAKER_03] Ne, ne, ne, ne,

626
00:27:53,839 --> 00:27:55,599
[SPEAKER_03] ne trao mi pola sata.

627
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:57,180
[SPEAKER_03] Ne znam, ne znam ti točno reći,

628
00:27:57,180 --> 00:27:58,259
[SPEAKER_03] mogu samo nagađat.

629
00:27:58,259 --> 00:27:59,759
[SPEAKER_03] To je, to je, ovaj,

